&lt;p&gt;Is there any way for have them show up in both?&lt;/p&gt;
 </title><link>https://faq.i3wm.org/question/847/system-tray-icons-are-on-the-wrong-display/?answer=848#post-id-848</link><description>Yes, there is a way to specify on which monitor the tray icons should appear: http://i3wm.org/docs/userguide.html#_tray_output

